  <title>Add Motion-Path FB</title>
  <meta name="DESCRIPTION" translate="true" value="A Motion-Path FB has many uses. It can define the path of a Robot, a Belt or Chain, and also provide the input for Ram-R and Ram-P Dyads. Example applications of the Ram-R dyad is the extending cylinder that are used by Scissor-Lifts." />
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Add<keyword>Function-Block: Motion-Path</keyword></keyword>
    <keyword>Function-Block<keyword>Motion-Path FB</keyword></keyword>
    <keyword>Motion-Path Function-Block</keyword>
    <keyword>Ram-P dyad</keyword>
    <keyword>Ram-R dyad (Scissor-Lift Cyclinder)</keyword>
    <keyword>Robot Path</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Add Motion-Path FB</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2" style="page-break-before:always;">Motion-Path FB</para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See also <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-FunctionBlock-MotionPath">Motion-Path dialog</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">Terminology and Definitions</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:164px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" style="text-align:right;">Motion-Path FB : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">FB</text> that adds a <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Motion-Point</text> to a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">sketch-path </text>- see <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Sketch-Loop" styleclass="VariableName-small">sketch-loop</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:164px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box2" style="text-align:right;">Motion-Point : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The motion-values at the input to the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Motion-Path FB</text> control the motion of the <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Motion-Point</text> along the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">sketch-path</text>.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">Example applications of a Motion-Path FB:</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">To control the motion of a robot along a sketch-path</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">To control the motion of a chain or belt along a sketch-path</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">To control the motion of an extending-cylinder to raise a Scissor-Lift</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Add Motion-Path FB</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="3" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:68px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName">Add : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
