                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="Element">Motion-Path FB</text> is now in <text styleclass="Body Text">the graphic-area</text> (and <text styleclass="Interface">Assembly-Tree</text>).</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">AND</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">A <text styleclass="VariableName">Motion-Point</text> is at the <text styleclass="Interface">start-Point</text> of the sketch-element you click on the sketch-path<text styleclass="BodyText BI">.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
