          <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-align:center;">SUMMARY</para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; background-color:#fbfbfb;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-align:center;">Motion-Point is constrained by a sketch-element and motion-data controls its position, velocity, and acceleration</para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; background-color:#fbfbfb;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-align:center;">A Motion-Part is constrained by a joint and motion-data controls its position, velocity, and acceleration.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
